thread.title: Porsche' C.

author: Porsche' C.
title: Porsche' C.
text: I like this company. Out of the few companies that sell my contact brand, this company is the cheapist! The ordering process was easy and there were many convenient ways to get my prescription to them. My contacts were on back order (they are fairly new to the market) and I did end up paying the post office extra money to pick up my package but luckily it was less than $1.50. Overall I would recommend this company to others and I'd consider myself to be return customer.
